  09 Jun 2009; Peter Alfredsen <loki_val@gentoo.org> mono-2.0.9999.ebuild,
  mono-2.2.9999.ebuild, mono-2.4.9999.ebuild, mono-9999.ebuild:
  Drop keywords for all *9999 ebuilds instead of maintaining a huge
  package.mask

